overview.en: ThinkBit Pro is a Next Gen cryptocurrency exchange, which offers an excellent liquid trading environment, a 100% cold storage of crypto assets, a variety of order types and a high performance API for professional traders.
overview.zh: ThinkBit Pro 是下一代的数字资产交易所，为专业用户提供高流动性交易环境、全资产冷储存、多种订单类、高性能 API。ThinkBit Pro 使用自研的粒子对撞交易撮合引擎，处理订单速度达500万订单/秒/交易对；绝对零度100%冷钱包技术，保护用户数字资产安全。
